    "summary": "During slickline operations on 4 February 2021 at 02:30 hours at Baldpate Platform, a Retrieve Subsurface (RS) retrieval tool unexpectedly released from a fished tool string while being lowered to the deck. The tool fell 6-8 inches, struck a light plant, and bounced into the red zone striking an injured party on the left leg, causing a 1.5-inch laceration requiring six stitches.",
